ChooseParameter.Other: Then, the resultant acid-treated GnP was col- lected on a polytetrafluoroethylene filter (Advantec, Japan; H050A047A) with a pore size of 0.22 mm and washed with a large amount of deionized water until the pH of colature reached about 7.

Mixing.Description: The hardener was added to the GnP/epoxy mixture at a ratio of 14.5:100.
